*   **IP Geolocation:** The discussion on future architectural principles regarding location vs. routing will continue on the `architecture-discuss@iab.org` mailing list.
*   **AI Considerations:** The IAB will monitor the community's interest in formalizing AI considerations for protocol development, following discussions in the CATALYST BOF.